Review only PM-133, PM-134, PM-135 in pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx. Approve/reject/improve these findings only: 1) openHelpDrawer lacks currentTableId redirect to setShowTableConfirmSheet(true); 2) "Другое" textarea uses CSS collapse instead of conditional render; 3) textarea lacks autoFocus; 4) submit button is inside scrollable collapsible block instead of sticky bottom action area; 5) openHelpDrawer does not reset helpQuickSent/sendingCardId/showOtherForm/helpComment on reopen. Output concise markdown with Approved Findings, Rejected Findings, Improved Findings, New Scoped Findings, Summary.
